article_id:1830,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia Remix!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia Remix will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1608012000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>Limited-time adventurers will appear in Gala Dragalia. The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: Adventurers added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase as well. For information about which adventurers may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><br>Note: Until now, the example summoning rates given in the Details tab of the Showcase Info section of each summon showcase have been based on rates that match those of that specific summon showcase. Beginning with this summon showcase, however, the example summoning rates given will be general values for explanatory purposes not dependent on each individual showcase.<br></span></div><hr><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>■If a 5★ does not appear after 10 summons, the 5★ Appearance Rate for the next summon increases by 0.5%.</strong></span></div><hr><div><br></div><div>Newly added limited-time featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Dragonyule Lily (water/staff)</div><div>5★ Dragonyule Victor (shadow/axe)</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer from past Gala Dragalia summon showcases:</div><div>5★ Gala Sarisse (flame/bow)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia Remix event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1608012000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1608271199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurers:</div><div>
